Waiting Placement  true false
Studying           true false


if     NOT Waiting Placement    and      NOT Studying        == former student ( >1 year, archive )
if         Waiting Placement    and      NOT Studying        == new student or returning student
if     NOT Waiting Placement    and          Studying        == current student
if         Waiting Placement    and          Studying        == continuing student



     
